12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 22 O.S. 2021, Section 1325, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 1325. A. Any sheriff's office or campus police agency
16 as authorized under the Oklahoma Campus Security Act is authorized
17 to dispose of by public sale, destruction, donation, or transfer for
18 use to a governmental subdivision personal property which has come
19 into its possession, or deposit in a special fund, as hereafter
20 provided, all money or legal tender of the United States which has
21 come into its possession, whether the property or money be stolen,
22 embezzled, lost, abandoned or otherwise, the owner of the property
23 or money being unknown or not having claimed the same, and which the
24 sheriff or campus police agency has held for at least six (6)
